content:
Check:
  all:
    - name: IETESTCD
      operator: is_not_contained_by
      value: $ti_ietestcd
Operations:
  - operator: distinct
    domain: TI
    name: IETESTCD
    id: $ti_ietestcd
Core:
  Id: CORE-000228
  Version: '1'
  Status: Published
Description: Check if IETESTCD is present in TI.IETESTCD
Outcome:
  Message: IETESTCD from IE domain does not exist in IETESTCD of TI domain.
  Output Variables:
    - IETESTCD
Rule Type: Record Data
Sensitivity: Record
Authorities:
  - Organization: CDISC
    Standards:
      - Name: SDTMIG
        Version: '3.4'
        References:
          - Origin: SDTM and SDTMIG Conformance Rules
            Rule Identifier:
              Id: CG0179
              Version: '1'
            Version: '2.0'
            Citations:
              - Cited Guidance: The complete list of Inclusion/Exclusion criteria
                  can be found in the Trial Inclusion/Exclusion Criteria (TI) dataset
                  described in Section 7.4.1, Trial Inclusion/Exclusion Criteria.
                Document: IG v3.4
                Item: Specification
                Section: 6.3.4
Scope:
  Classes:
    Include:
      - FINDINGS
  Domains:
    Include:
      - IE
